<paragraph blockId="197.[189,1398,423,555]" pageId="197" pageNumber="198">
Four sequences available (BOLD process IDs: BOWMT260-10, BOWMT377-10, BOWMT400-10, BOWMT401-10; BIN: BOLD:AAU5301). 
<taxonomicName authority="Gardner &amp; Gibbs, 2020" authorityName="Gardner &amp; Gibbs" authorityYear="2020" box="[700,952,458,484]" class="Insecta" family="Halictidae" genus="Lasioglossum" kingdom="Animalia" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="197" pageNumber="198" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="torrens" status="sp. nov.">
